{"tid":2165558,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中駐美大使崔天凱警告美國：「『鐘為誰鳴』，將來會有算帳的一天。」","createTime":"2020-08-20T01:55:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-20T03:57:14.000Z","uid":184679,"like":9,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"8b06bec5bd5b4f4ca9aac4bb51cd72cc8612d5b2","tid":2165558,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T01:55:41.000Z","msg":"大陸駐美大使崔天凱日前在布魯金斯學會發表演說時警告，即便冷戰期間也發生過韓戰和越戰兩場熱戰，使美國及相關國家付出慘痛代價。中美是要合作推動「後疫情世界」建設，或陷入「修昔底德陷阱」，美國必須作出根本性的選擇。<br />\n<br />\n他指出，美國一些人如此沈迷於「冷戰」一詞，或許是認為他們曾贏得冷戰，但不應忘記世界為40多年冷戰付出的代價。如果中美關係的負面趨勢繼續發展，中國可能面臨更多困難和挑戰，但「新冷戰」的發起者也必須仔細掂量自己將付出的代價，以及給世界帶來的災禍。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/08/20/realtime/8396247.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=800&amp;exp=3600&amp;w=465\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F08%2F20%2Frealtime%2F8396247.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D800%26exp%3D3600%26w%3D465&h=6413d06f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n路透<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/7331/4795771?from=udn-catelistnews_ch2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F7331%2F4795771%3Ffrom%3Dudn-catelistnews_ch2&d=MESMej01p5OZpZHaxDRufXO%2BoULzyGumsBrFMfYiBSk%3D&h=2f18b6fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/7331/4795771?from=udn-catelistnews_ch2</a>"},{"pid":"1bbe1e28e64e7c89eec85480486cf0db68a0db8b","tid":2165558,"uid":82532,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T01:57:17.000Z","msg":"他指出，美國一些人如此沈迷於「冷戰」一詞<br />\n美國好鍾意講&quot;cold war&quot;咩, 係口交部先開口「冷戰思維」埋口「冷戰思維」"},{"pid":"94625da7ff57aa63f7490228c82b99837bccc277","tid":2165558,"uid":271894,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T02:03:31.000Z","msg":"自己敲喪鐘 仲要叫人敲大力d"},{"pid":"71731e653b16f0d1c7e37857330f0af951f2b2ab","tid":2165558,"uid":261388,"lik